      Implemented as specialization of XMeans.

      class  KMediansLloyd<V extends NumberVector>
      k-medians clustering algorithm, but using Lloyd-style bulk iterations instead of the more complicated approach suggested by Kaufman and Rousseeuw (see PAM instead).
      class  LloydKMeans<V extends NumberVector>
      The standard k-means algorithm, using bulk iterations and commonly attributed to Lloyd and Forgy (independently).
      class  MacQueenKMeans<V extends NumberVector>

      class  ShallotKMeans<V extends NumberVector>

      class  SingleAssignmentKMeans<V extends NumberVector>

      class  SortMeans<V extends NumberVector>

      class  XMeans<V extends NumberVector,​M extends MeanModel>
